npm install genlayer-js
import { GenLayerClient } from "genlayer-js";


const client = new GenLayerClient({ network: "local" });
const contract = await client.getContract("DisputeResolution");

await contract.call("submit_claim", {
sender: userAddress,
claim: "Work was completed as agreed"
});

const state = await contract.state();
console.log(state.winner);

UX Tip

Design UIs that:

Show pending states

Explain what validators are deciding

Do not assume instant finality
